1
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,760
(Episode 26)

2
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,640
Whenever you see each other,

3
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:38,160
you two can't quite handle
your feelings for each other.

4
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,040
Isn't that right?

5
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,200
Yes, you are right.

6
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:45,040
A Yan, deep down in your heart

7
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,880
do you somehow

8
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,200
hate Xiaomeng?

9
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
Because of the hatred,

10
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,400
there are many things

11
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:55,400
that you can't see and understand.

12
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:58,000
But I believe one day

13
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,240
you will figure it out.

14
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:02,600
By then, there will be no barriers
between the two of you anymore.

15
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,720
I also wish for such a day.

16
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,880
No matter what the future holds,

17
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,920
you will always love Xiaomeng, won't you?

18
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,400
Aunt Lin,

19
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,200
I should leave now.

20
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,800
I will visit you again.

21
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,600
-Brother.
-Tiankong.

22
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,560
I have to go.

23
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,520
Brother A Yan,

24
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,880
will you visit me again?

25
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,080
Of course.

26
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,160
How about tomorrow?

27
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,720
If you have time tomorrow,

28
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,400
can you come and play with me?

29
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,240
Sure.

30
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,520
Tiankong.

31
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,240
The ring necklace on your neck...

32
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,960
The ring necklace is...

33
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,040
a gift from Xiaomeng.

34
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,800
Tiankong,

35
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,760
brother A Yan should leave now.

36
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,440
Say goodbye to him.

37
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,920
Goodbye, brother.

38
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,200
Goodbye.

39
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,360
Madam Lin,

40
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:27,880
didn't you give me the ring necklace?

41
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,600
Why did you tell brother A Yan

42
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,320
that it's from Miss Xiaomeng?

43
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,120
I'm telling you, Tiankong.

44
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:40,640
This really is a gift from both me
and Miss Xiaomeng.

45
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,680
From now on, if anyone asks,

46
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,000
you should tell them
it's a gift from Xiaomeng. Understood?

47
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,560
I understand, Madam Lin.

48
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,000
Can we play the remote control helicopter
for a little longer?

49
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,480
Sure, go and play.

50
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,200
Every time I drive you home,

51
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,800
I wish you could live farther from me.

52
00:04:21,280 --> 00:04:23,200
Then I can spend more time with you.

53
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,680
It's very late. You should go home soon.

54
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:29,400
I had a great time today.

55
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,400
Xiaomeng,

56
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,080
don't you worry too much about work.

57
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:35,000
I believe there would be

58
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,000
many job invitations for you in a week.

59
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,360
I have told you

60
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,360
I don't want to rely on others,

61
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:43,040
or get jobs by cronyism.

62
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,160
How is that the case?

63
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,440
You are very talented.

64
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,680
Why would you need cronyism?

65
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,640
You only need to stay in good shape,

66
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,760
and I can't think of
any company that would reject you.

67
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,480
Why do you always have such faith in me?

68
00:04:56,880 --> 00:05:00,080
Because I am your number one fan.

69
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,520
All right. I'm going in.

70
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,600
You should go home now.

71
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,080
Safe journey.

72
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,320
Xiaomeng,

73
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,120
you have wetted my clothes
with tears today.

74
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,440
How could you turn me away so hastily?

75
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,000
Come and give me a hug.

76
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,120
Comfort me.

77
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,920
Xiaomeng,

78
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,440
let's have dessert together next time.

79
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,080
Sure.

80
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,040
A Yan.

81
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,760
You seem to be in a good mood.

82
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,400
I'm all right.

83
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,240
You had a date with Jiang Ze, didn't you?

84
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,160
I didn't.

85
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,040
I just bumped into him on the way.

86
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,240
I had a chat with him

87
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,920
and he gave me a ride.

88
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,680
Where did you go to bump into him?

89
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,040
I was looking for jobs

90
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,400
and bumped into him on the way.

91
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,560
Don't get it wrong.

92
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,640
I didn't get anything wrong.

93
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,880
I really bumped into him on the way.

94
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,960
We are just friends.

95
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,800
A Yan,

96
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,320
is that a problem to you?

97
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,360
Zhou Xiaomeng,

98
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,760
I don't want to listen to you anymore.

99
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,480
You are very smart,

100
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,160
especially good at feigning innocence
and being miserable.

101
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:05,240
Only a childish man like Jiang Ze
would be attracted by you.

102
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,520
Don't worry.

103
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,000
I won't be enchanted by you.

104
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,040
Zhou Yanzhao, what do you mean?

105
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,960
How did I ever feign in front of you?

106
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,560
You feigned your devotion to me,

107
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:23,800
yet you were in Jiang Ze's arms
soon enough.

108
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,720
Do you want me to applaud
your performance?

109
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,720
We've known each other since childhood.

110
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,840
In front of you, I could
pretend for one day or one month.

111
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,480
Could I have pretended all these years?

112
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:37,640
Do you not know what kind of person I am?

113
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,640
You have changed

114
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,800
and you think everyone has changed.
Am I right?

115
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,960
Good. Let me ask you.

116
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,720
Where is the ring necklace
that I gave you?

117
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,360
I...

118
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,840
You gave it to someone else.

119
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,800
Shouldn't you have at least told me first?

120
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,320
Tiankong? You saw Tiankong--

121
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,360
Yes,

122
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,200
I do wish Tiankong could recover soon.

123
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,960
But you know that the ring necklace

124
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,000
was the only gift
from my mom before she died.

125
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,480
You know it means a lot to me.

126
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,760
Yet you gave it away anyway.

127
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,520
At least you should have told me.

128
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,600
It's not like that.

129
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,840
-I...
-Xiaomeng, A Yan.

130
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,480
What are you fighting about?

131
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,360
Take it easy.

132
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,720
Mom, I'm not fighting with A Yan.

133
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:21,160
It's only a misunderstanding. It's fine.

134
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:24,640
I heard you mentioned a ring.

135
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,080
Give it back to A Yan.

136
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,240
I have many jewelry.

137
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,800
I will give you anything you want.

138
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,680
It's not like that.

139
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,760
Go back in your room and rest.

140
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:39,640
Well, A Yan...

141
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,040
I will ask Xiaomeng
to give you back the stuff.

142
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,520
Don't be angry.

143
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,160
Be good.

144
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,320
A Yan.

145
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,400
Listen to me.

146
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,640
♪ Pounding breaths ♪

147
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,760
♪ Innocent sweetness ♪

148
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,520
♪ Used to be ♪

149
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:20,240
♪ The secrets that we shared ♪

150
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,880
♪ The path of life ♪

151
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,320
♪ Was rippled because of you ♪

152
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:33,760
♪ Once I thought about leaving everything
for you ♪

153
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,040
I've kept this badge...

154
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,720
close to my heart all these years.

155
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,400
She's been watching over me.

156
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,960
She's never left my side.

157
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:49,080
All right, I trust you.

158
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:53,360
♪ Crashing our world ♪

159
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:56,520
♪ Into smithereens and pieces ♪

160
00:09:56,800 --> 00:10:01,800
♪ How can I edit my memories ♪

161
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:05,000
♪ All my love for you ♪

162
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:09,320
♪ And all the feelings that we share ♪

163
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,200
♪ Will be completely covered ♪

164
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:17,160
♪ Switching off my reliance on you ♪

165
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:20,880
♪ No matter how sorrowful it is ♪

166
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:24,400
♪ No matter how hopeless it is ♪

167
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:29,280
♪ If only I can prove that I existed ♪

168
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,480
Anything else?

169
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:40,000
I'm turning in if there's nothing else.

170
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,000
Sit down!

171
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,920
I haven't finished yet.
Why are you leaving?

172
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,800
Look at you, a grown-up!

173
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,880
How come you can't keep anything in mind?

174
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,240
I need you now!

175
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,360
Just tell me anything.

176
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,880
Am I not obedient enough to you?

177
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,200
I want to ask you.

178
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,880
How has my plan to transfer you
to the Dikai Commercial City project

179
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:05,840
been progressing?

180
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,320
It's just a simple task.

181
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,800
I've got it done by just asking.

182
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,160
I don't know what's the big deal.

183
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:12,680
Are you saying that...

184
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,840
Zhou Yanzhao has agreed?

185
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,080
He has agreed,

186
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,400
but he wants me
to take care of both projects,

187
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,960
and asked me to learn from you.

188
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,160
I don't know
what I can learn from you though.

189
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,640
Both projects?

190
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:30,200
What is on Zhou Yanzhao's mind?

191
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,440
I just don't get
what you are fighting for.

192
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:34,880
Isn't it great that

193
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,040
Shenghai makes money and then we share it?

194
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,680
It belongs to me.
No one else can touch it!

195
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,760
I have to get it back
even if I have to fight to the death.

196
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,320
That is your stuff.

197
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,520
What have I got to do with it?

198
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,840
How are you not related?

199
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,680
Am I not doing all this for you?

200
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,920
You're just fooling around all the time.

201
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,120
If only you could
quit some of your bad habits

202
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,200
and work harder on everything,

203
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,240
do I need to do so much work?

204
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,160
Dad,

205
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,240
I'm tired of your speech.

206
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,520
I'll say it again.

207
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,840
You are you and I am me.

208
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,240
Fine.

209
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,680
If you have to draw a line between us,

210
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,480
I won't say one more word.

211
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:18,520
You now have your hands in
the Dikai Commercial City project.

212
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,680
I want to know

213
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:22,080
if you have done anything today

214
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:24,040
to get yourself ready for the project.

215
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,000
Today...

216
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,480
Xiaomeng was in trouble today.

217
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,400
I gave her a hand.

218
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:31,960
Are you saying that

219
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,880
you had a date with Zhou Xiaomeng?

220
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,280
What? Is there a problem?

221
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,960
It's a good thing that
you and Xiaomeng are going out.

222
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,240
You have my full support.

223
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,960
I really don't get you.

224
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,600
But I'm telling you,

225
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,360
leave my business alone.

226
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,120
You brat!

227
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,600
A Yan!

228
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,160
A Yan!

229
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,600
A Yan!

230
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:25,920
A Yan!

231
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,800
A Yan, I'm sorry

232
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,200
I've woken you up.

233
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,440
What's the matter?

234
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:35,680
A Yan,

235
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,480
please forgive Xiaomeng.

236
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,120
I've found

237
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,880
what you want.

238
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,640
Is it this thing?

239
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:50,840
Where did you find it?

240
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,200
It's right in her room.

241
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:55,240
Xiaomeng must be too careless.

242
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,440
It's in the deepest corner

243
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,840
of her drawer,

244
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,360
so she couldn't find it.

245
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:02,280
I found it. Is it the one?

246
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,240
Xiaomeng

247
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:07,280
must have forgotten where she put it.

248
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,840
It's not her fault.

249
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:10,720
Now I've found it.

250
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,160
It can clarify

251
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,680
your misunderstanding.

252
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,120
You and Xiaomeng

253
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,520
have to get along well.

254
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,200
Be good. Listen to me.

255
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,400
Bye-bye.

256
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:54,400
A Yan,

257
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,640
you've turned 18 today.

258
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,640
I have some important thing for you.

259
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,120
This is a video tape

260
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,960
from your mother.

261
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,480
She told me

262
00:15:06,520 --> 00:15:08,840
to only give it to you
when you are 18 years old.

263
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,480
Now you can watch it.

264
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:57,480
A Yan, you are now 18,

265
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,480
an adult man now.

266
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:04,280
Mom wants to be with you,
and watch you grow up.

267
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,320
Unfortunately...

268
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:12,240
Sorry, I couldn't stop crying.

269
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:20,440
Before I started filming, I told myself

270
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:23,240
I couldn't let you see me cry, but...

271
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,480
Dad,

272
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,200
you still don't want to
see my mom even now?

273
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,120
Even in the video?

274
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:49,120
My company is in a dire predicament.

275
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,120
I have to handle it.

276
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:05,120
My dear A Yan,

277
00:17:06,840 --> 00:17:08,800
are you happy on your birthday?

278
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,240
Did Dad buy you a birthday cake?

279
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,360
I wonder...

