00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,200
that I can't see you grow up.

284
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:34,480
But I think...

285
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:39,440
you must still be that amazing boy, right?

286
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:44,880
I am sorry.

287
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,960
Yet I am happy

288
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,600
that you are my son.

289
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:54,760
I will always be proud of you.

290
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:58,760
Happy birthday.

291
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,160
Xiaomeng.

292
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,440
Are you going to visit Tiankong now?

293
00:18:58,840 --> 00:18:59,800
I'm going to the hospital

294
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,360
