302
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:20,760
Tell them

303
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,800
I'll visit Tiankong when I have time.

304
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:23,720
Sure.

305
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:53,880
Tiankong.

306
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:54,920
Brother A Yan,

307
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,280
