308
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,480
Yes.

309
00:19:57,760 --> 00:20:01,080
I've even brought you some gifts
which are from Xiaomeng.

310
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:05,320
Tiankong,

311
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,520
why are you alone here?

312
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:08,920
Where is Director Lin?

313
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:11,160
Madam Lin is with the doctor.

314
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,640
She'll be back soon.

315
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:18,800
Tiankong,

316
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:21,760
can you tell me

317
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:23,920
who gave you that?

318
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:26,480
Madam Lin gave me this,

319
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:28,240
but Madam Lin asked me to say that

320
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,520
it's from Miss Xiaomeng.

321
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:33,440
Madam Lin told me not to tell anyone.

322
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:36,880
Tiankong, don't worry.

323
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,120
I'll keep the secret for you.

324
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,680
Can you take it off
and let me have a look?

325
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:08,400
Tiankong,

326
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:12,480
can you keep it to yourself that
you took this off...

327
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,400
and showed it to me?

328
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,600
We each have a secret.

329
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,120
We each have a secret.

330
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,640
Pinky swear.

331
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:23,600
Whoever tells the others is the bad boy.

332
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:24,840
Good.

333
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:31,840
A Yan,

334
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,240
what are you doing here?

335
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:38,640
Xiaomeng has been held up by business

336
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,400
so she told me to send Tiankong some toys.

337
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:43,280
Tiankong,

338
00:21:43,360 --> 00:21:44,800
you've got some new toys.

339
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,160
Yes, I have new toys.

340
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:49,600
-I...
-I...

341
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:55,000
I'm going to take Tiankong for a check-up.

342
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:58,800
I should return to the company.

343
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:03,200
Then I'll see you out.

344
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,040
Sure.

345
00:22:08,120 --> 00:22:08,920
See you, Tiankong.

346
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:10,040
Brother A Yan,

347
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:11,720
you must visit me again.

348
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:12,840
Sure.

349
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:21,840
Aunt Lin,

350
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,320
goodbye.

351
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:26,240
Goodbye.

352
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,760
I wonder what's special about today.

353
00:22:48,840 --> 00:22:49,960
So many people have given birth today.

354
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:54,640
I haven't even stopped to drink water
since last night.

355
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:56,400
I'm telling you,

356
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,280
no matter how busy you are,

357
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:59,000
