on the bracelets on the newborns.

358
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,200
Don't mix them up,

359
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:03,200
otherwise, there'd be
unimaginable consequences.

360
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:06,360
You're right. No matter how tough it is,

361
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,600
we have to be responsible.

362
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,920
We can't be careless even for a second.

363
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:11,040
We can never mix up the children

364
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,160
otherwise, it'd ruin two families.

