370
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:22,880
(Uncle Fang)

371
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,000
Yan.

372
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,240
Uncle Fang.

373
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:37,280
A Yan,

374
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:39,200
do you miss me?

375
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:43,840
Uncle Fang, I want to ask you something.

376
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,960
When I was born,

377
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,520
neither you nor Dad was by my mom's side.

378
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:50,720
A Yan,

379
00:24:51,080 --> 00:24:52,680
why are you bringing this up?

380
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:54,920
Did Xiaomeng say something to you?

381
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,200
Did Xiaomeng ask about that too?

382
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,560
She...

383
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:04,520
She gave me a call
and asked me a few questions.

384
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:06,960
What really happened at the time?

385
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,440
You were born in Sydney.

386
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,520
Boss and I were

387
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:14,280
in Shanghai dealing with a big project,

388
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,120
so we were not by your mom's side.

389
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:19,840
I don't know what exactly happened there.

390
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:22,400
Your mom was not well

391
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:24,280
and she had miscarriages a few times.

392
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:27,480
When she was carrying you,

393
00:25:27,760 --> 00:25:30,320
your dad sent your mom
to Sydney for a quiet rest.

394
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:33,080
When your dad knew that
you were safely born,

395
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,880
he was so thrilled.

396
00:25:36,560 --> 00:25:37,760
So when I was born,

397
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:39,920
neither of you was with my mom.

398
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:41,880
That's right.

399
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,040
Uncle Fang,

400
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:50,840
I see.

401
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,360
Take care.

402
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,360
I'll visit you when I have time.

403
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:20,240
(International Departures Information)

404
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:21,120
Qingyan,

405
00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:23,080
I'll be in Sydney for a few days
to take care of something.

406
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:24,760
Keep it to yourself. Don't tell anyone.

407
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:26,680
For the business of Shenghai,
if it's not particularly important,

408
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:27,680
you may handle it by yourself.

409
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:39,640
(Piano Concert)

410
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,360
(Shenghai Group)

411
00:26:43,280 --> 00:26:44,080
Come in.

412
00:26:56,600 --> 00:26:57,400
Where is Chairman Zhou?

413
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,280
Isn't he back yet?

414
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,720
Yesterday he said that

415
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:03,240
he had something to take care of
these few days.

416
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,240
You startled me, Lingxi.

417
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,560
Come on. Do you get startled so easily?

418
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:15,320
Where do you think Chairman Zhou is?

419
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:16,920
He didn't say.

420
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,760
Do you have anything to tell him urgently?

421
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,800
Today there's a meeting with
the contractors.

422
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:23,800
Didn't he tell you?

423
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,400
The contractors?

424
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,840
Let me check.

425
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:30,560
You forgot about it
and you need to check the schedule?

426
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,440
I saw it now.

427
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:35,600
The meeting with the contractors

428
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,560
has been postponed to next week.

429
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:37,800
We have notified them already.

430
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,920
What is so important that
Chairman Zhou has to handle it

431
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,200
in these few days?

432
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:46,320
I don't know that either.

433
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:52,680
Well...

434
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:55,640
my friend gave me two tickets

435
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,880
to a piano concert.

436
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,560
I don't know whom I should go with.

437
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:01,480
Are you interested?

438
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:03,600
Forget it.

439
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:05,200
There's so much work to do.
I need to work overtime tonight.

440
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:06,280
I can't find the time to go.

441
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:08,040
Overtime?

442
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:09,360
I can help you.

443
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:10,880
I'm not very busy anyway.

444
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:13,520
I don't want to trouble you.
I can handle it.

445
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:24,000
(Piano Concert)

446
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,440
(Piano Concert)

447
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:19,200
Qingyan, why are you still here?

448
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,480
You are a tough lady indeed.

449
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,080
You're still working hard at this hour.

450
00:29:25,320 --> 00:29:26,360
Do you have to work so hard?

451
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:29,600
Even though Chairman Zhou is not here,
I can't stop working.

452
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:30,880
Aren't you working overtime too?

453
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,680
I haven't finished my work in hand.

454
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,040
I thought I could

455
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:40,320
go to the concert with you today.

456
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:41,920
I am a bit hungry.

457
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:42,800
Have you had dinner yet?

458
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,280
Not yet.

459
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:46,440
How about I buy you dinner?

460
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,800
But I have not finished
my work for the project yet.

461
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,720
How about takeaway?

462
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:52,600
Sure.

463
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:54,080
What do you want to eat? I will order.

464
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:55,480
Anything.

465
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:56,560
Order anything for me please.

466
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:58,840
-Good.
-I will carry on with my work then.

467
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,040
Wait for me at your office.

468
00:30:00,080 --> 00:30:01,720
Let's eat together when the food is here.

469
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,240
Go on working then. I'll order.

470
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:04,200
-Just a minute.
-Sure.

471
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,320
What did you say?

472
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:49,320
You...

473
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,960
calm down.

474
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:54,840
If you want,

475
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:58,040
your child can come back to life.

476
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:03,560
Really?

477
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:37,640
I'm very sorry
to let you know it like this.

478
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,400
At that time,

479
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:42,600
the doctor was in jail
because of this incident.

480
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,040
Is there anyone behind all this?

481
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,320
You can think of it that way.

482
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:52,200
My mom's last name is Lin.

483
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:54,080
Yueling Lin.

484
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,360
That's right.

485
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:00,880
Why would anyone

486
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:02,800
abandon her own child?

487
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,040
I'm sorry, sir.

488
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:08,800
That's all I know. I'm very sorry.

489
00:32:31,320 --> 00:32:33,400
Zhen, what's the matter with you today?

490
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,040
What else can it be?

491
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:37,240
Of course it's your superstar classmate.

492
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:39,440
I set up the schedule,

493
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:40,800
and she wouldn't follow it,

494
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,560
insisting on doing it her own way.

495
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,240
All right, then I let her.

496
00:32:44,560 --> 00:32:45,400
And?

497
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:47,640
Today our supervisor examined the clips.

498
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:51,640
That episode was harshly criticized.

499
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:53,320
Now she wouldn't admit it

500
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:55,440
and she put all the blame on me.

501
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,680
Tell me what I can do.

502
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,840
Zhen, it was I

503
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:03,400
who introduced her to you after all.

504
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:05,720
However, I had no idea

505
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:07,280
she would be so difficult to work with.

506
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:09,800
It's not your fault.

507
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:11,400
One thing has nothing to do
with the other.

508
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:14,520
You can't take responsibility
for the mistakes she made.

509
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:16,560
Right.

510
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,040
How are Tiankong's eyes?

511
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,640
He is recovering quite well.

512
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:22,200
He should be able to go home in a while.

513
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,600
How about you?

514
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:27,320
Have you made any progress with Dr. Xiao?

515
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:30,760
I...

516
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,160
What's wrong?

517
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:38,680
We are too busy.

518
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:42,000
We can hardly find the time to meet.

519
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,840
He...

520
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,080
How is he?

521
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,120
Has he never been

522
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:54,080
in a romantic relation before?

523
00:33:55,560 --> 00:33:56,520
Really?

524
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:59,800
I have never asked him

525
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:02,040
such a personal question.

526
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,400
I wonder

527
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:05,640
if he even knows
how to be in a romantic relationship,

528
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:07,280
and what a romantic relationship
is supposed to be.

529
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,680
For example,

530
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,440
I said that my hands were cold.

531
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,400
It's an obvious hint.

532
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:14,360
He immediately bought
a cup of hot milk tea

533
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,280
for me to hold in my hands.

534
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,800
Let me give you another example.

535
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,000
We went to see a movie.

536
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:21,280
The lightning was perfect,
and the atmosphere too.

537
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,200
I just laid my head a bit on him,

538
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,560
then he moved away at once

539
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,800
and sat very straight.

540
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:29,560
He looked like a gentleman
not to be tempted at all.

541
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,360
What do you think I should do?

542
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:35,000
Zhen,

543
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:38,200
you have just started
going out for a few days.

544
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:41,040
And you said there was no time for dates.

545
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:44,960
How come you have already touched hands
and leaned on his shoulder?

546
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:47,240
You are moving too fast.

547
00:34:49,720 --> 00:34:51,680
I am not moving fast.

548
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,440
Isn't it how...

549
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,960
all relationships develop?

550
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:01,840
Moreover, I am not asking for a lot.

551
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:05,680
I just think he should
treat me like a woman.

552
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:07,400
Show me some response.

553
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,720
Right. I get it.

554
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,800
Dr. Xiao is usually

555
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:15,240
a serious person.

556
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:17,200
But relationships

557
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,800
have to grow naturally.

558
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:19,960
You can't force it.

559
